pre_pr_migrator_status.python311: not solvable (bot CI job): main: ['osx_arm64_python3.8.____cpython: Encountered problems while solving:\n - package pyobjc-framework-quartz-7.3-py39h2804cbe_0 requires python >=3.9,<3.10.0a0, but none of the providers can be installed\n']

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "inputs" %}
{% set version = "0.5" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/inputs-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a31d5b96a3525f1232f326be9e7ce8ccaf873c6b1fb84d9f3c9bc3d79b23eae4

build:
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 2

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - pyobjc-framework-quartz  # [osx]

test:
  imports:
    - inputs
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/zeth/inputs
  summary: Cross-platform Python support for keyboards, mice and gamepads.
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Tobias-Fischer
